<div class="page-returns pt-nav">

  <div class="page-hero" style="position:relative;height:40vh;min-height:300px;overflow:hidden;background:#1a1a1a;">
    <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;text-align:center;padding:2rem;">
      <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3.5rem);color:#fff;margin-bottom:1rem;letter-spacing:0.05em;">Returns & Exchanges</h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.05rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);max-width:500px;">Our commitment to your complete satisfaction</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section style="padding:5rem 0;background:#fff;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;">

      <div style="margin-bottom:3.5rem;">
        <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:1.6rem;margin-bottom:1.25rem;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e5e5;padding-bottom:0.75rem;">Return Policy</h2>
        <p style="color:var(--color-text-muted);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem;">
          We stand behind the quality of every DIAZ product. If you are not completely satisfied with your purchase, we accept returns within <strong>30 days</strong> of the delivery date.
        </p>
        <p style="color:var(--color-text-muted);line-height:1.8;">
          Items must be returned in their original condition — unworn, unused, with all original packaging and tags attached. We reserve the right to refuse returns that do not meet these criteria.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom:3.5rem;">
        <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:1.6rem;margin-bottom:1.25rem;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e5e5;padding-bottom:0.75rem;">How to Return</h2>
        <ol style="color:var(--color-text-muted);line-height:1.8;padding-left:1.25rem;">
          <li style="margin-bottom:1rem;">Contact our customer service team at <a href="/pages/contact" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;">contact us</a> with your order number and reason for return.</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:1rem;">Our team will provide you with a Return Merchandise Authorization (RMA) number and return instructions within 1–2 business days.</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:1rem;">Securely package the item(s) and include your RMA number on the outside of the package.</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:1rem;">Ship the package to the address provided. We recommend using a trackable shipping method.</li>
          <li>Once we receive and inspect the return, we will process your refund or exchange within 5–7 business days.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom:3.5rem;">
        <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:1.6rem;margin-bottom:1.25rem;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e5e5;padding-bottom:0.75rem;">Exchanges</h2>
        <p style="color:var(--color-text-muted);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem;">
          We are happy to exchange your item for a different size or color, subject to availability. To request an exchange, follow the same process as a return and specify the item you would like in its place.
        </p>
        <p style="color:var(--color-text-muted);line-height:1.8;">
          If the requested item is unavailable, we will issue a full refund to your original payment method.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom:3.5rem;">
        <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:1.6rem;margin-bottom:1.25rem;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e5e5;padding-bottom:0.75rem;">Non-Returnable Items</h2>
        <ul style="color:var(--color-text-muted);line-height:1.8;padding-left:1.25rem;">
          <li style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Custom or personalized items</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Items marked as final sale</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Items showing signs of use or wear</li>
          <li>Gift cards</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom:3.5rem;">
        <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:1.6rem;margin-bottom:1.25rem;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e5e5;padding-bottom:0.75rem;">Refunds</h2>
        <p style="color:var(--color-text-muted);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem;">
          Once your return is approved, refunds are processed to your original payment method within <strong>5–7 business days</strong>. Please allow additional time for your bank or credit card provider to process the credit.
        </p>
        <p style="color:var(--color-text-muted);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem;">
          All approved refunds are subject to a <strong>20% restocking fee</strong> deducted from the refund amount. This fee covers the cost of inspection, repackaging, and processing.
        </p>
        <p style="color:var(--color-text-muted);line-height:1.8;">
          Original shipping charges are non-refundable. Return shipping costs are the responsibility of the customer unless the return is due to a defect or our error.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="background:#f5f0ea;padding:2rem;border-radius:4px;">
        <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Have a Question?</h3>
        <p style="color:var(--color-text-muted);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem;">
          Our customer service team is here to help with any questions about returns or exchanges.
        </p>
        <a href="/pages/contact" style="display:inline-block;background:#1a1a1a;color:#fff;padding:0.75rem 2rem;font-size:0.85rem;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none;">Contact Us</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Returns Page",
  "tag": "div"
}
{% endschema %}
